title: PyPI Package Not Found
body:
(llm) shubhamsaboo@Shubham-Saboo's-Macbook-Pro ~ % pip install runai_model_streamer

ERROR: Could not find a version that satisfies the requirement runai_model_streamer (from versions: none)
ERROR: No matching distribution found for runai_model_streamer
author: Shubhamsaboo

comments.body:
Hey!
It's "runai-model-streamer" in PyPi.
In the code you should use "runai_model_streamer".

Just notice the mistake in the Readme, thanks for pointing that out!
